# Monitor setup

#
# Sets the default monitor orientation and position.
# This type of configuration is acceptable for a static context. For a laptop that is supposed to connect to different
# monitors it is best to create a script that recognises more precisely every monitor.

## Horizontal central monitor
#output DVI-I-1 scale 1
#output DVI-I-1 mode 1920x1080
#output DVI-I-1 pos 1080 520
#
## Vertical left monitor
#output HDMI-A-1 scale 1
#output HDMI-A-1 mode 1920x1080
#output HDMI-A-1 transform 270
#output HDMI-A-1 pos 0 0
